Subject: Make the progress bars show the relative effort that has been done
Issuer: Vincent Driessen <vincent@datafox.nl>
Date: 2009-05-20 08:21:03.230737
Type: feature
Priority: 3
Status: fixed
Assigned to: -

Every ticket should get a relative weight set (major change, minor change,
fix). According to this weight, the progress bars can give a more 'realistic'
feeling. For example, we can grade a major change 10x the size of a fix, and a
minor change 3 times the fix size.
